    "In 2016, Barton reinforced that notion by stating that the emerging technological culture is mainly compatible with the assumptions underlying PPL [45].",
    "In the same year, Barton and Haapio proposed a re-design of the legal system, which reconsiders the relationship between law and society, in order to guide a law reform in a technology-based society [46].",
